{"tid":2215282,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"自修GCE AL/IAL入大學好抵玩","createTime":"2020-09-24T01:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T16:10:56.000Z","uid":368082,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7ff1d713bc984feba1db0d10babd5aada8751b","tid":2215282,"uid":368082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:42:30.000Z","msg":"入到U幫人補習先接觸到英國AL syllabus<br />\n發覺AL syllabus同香港dse差唔多,最多深少少, 無以前香港AL咁難<br />\n<br />\n例如小弟有教人AL further maths, 難度同M2差唔多, 肯定淺過hkale pure maths<br />\n<br />\n連登成日話dse學制有濕鳩中文通識, 不利language廢數理勁既人<br />\n而家就有條明路, 經hkeaa以自修生身份報英國AL就得, 係香港考<br />\n<br />\n相比之下建議讀IAL &gt; GCE AL,<br />\n因爲IAL每年考兩次, 建議１月考唔好５月考, 如果考得好可以唔考dse, 直接non-jupas入U<br />\n<br />\n重點係用AL成績入U可以類似IB咁, 申請advanced standing, 可以提早一年畢業, 超正<br />\n又可以完美避左dse中文通識<br />\n例子: <a href=\"http://www.res.cuhk.edu.hk/images/content/undergraduate_student/year-1-student/core-requirements-and-exemption/core-course-exemption-by-attainment/admitted-with-advanced-standing/Framework-on-AS-2020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.res.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2Fundergraduate_student%2Fyear-1-student%2Fcore-requirements-and-exemption%2Fcore-course-exemption-by-attainment%2Fadmitted-with-advanced-standing%2FFramework-on-AS-2020.pdf&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=f5583773\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.res.cuhk.edu.hk/images/content/undergraduate_student/year-1-student/core-requirements-and-exemption/core-course-exemption-by-attainment/admitted-with-advanced-standing/Framework-on-AS-2020.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n如果以前知道咁既野, 就take IAL 英文+maths+further maths+physics/chem 啦<br />\n好過dse數理幾個5**, 中文通識３入唔到神科　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9545b6838d2b2d8937816ee6f4ebc59125560d","tid":2215282,"uid":358248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfd40ba00b8a77c8042f053c5d1b9a730465f8d7","tid":2215282,"uid":24