student/year-1-student/core-requirements-and-exemption/core-course-exemption-by-attainment/admitted-with-advanced-standing/Framework-on-AS-2020.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n如果以前知道咁既野, 就take IAL 英文+maths+further maths+physics/chem 啦<br />\n好過dse數理幾個5**, 中文通識３入唔到神科　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"講得出 take AL English Language<br />\n就知你唔熟個玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAL English難度一d 都唔低<br />\n<br />\n正確做法 係 take math + phy + chem + AS further/bio同考ielts"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"無講得清楚, 英文梗係讀AS啦, elective就讀AL<br />\n舊制HKALE都係中化UE AS, 其他elective多數讀AL"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />gce as level 英文你以為係HK As level UE個d咁容易？"},{"pid":"6407acb2043de838eeeb5c52b37b733737456a1f","tid":2215282,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"476483d2b0c7d306cccb9369510bab9c0f6c6fda","tid":2215282,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e474fb82f2b5699b85845a4769ae7d71a8719730","tid":2215282,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efadeef074f247ef2d3de5d136a4227cf16785a4","tid":2215282,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:52:19.000Z","msg":"英國除左d雞u都唔認啦<br />\n<br />\n你當佢地白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"咪當伴碟noju 個d 本身入到既其他hard subjects 都唔錯，你試下攞 AL中文 AL general studies同AL critical thinking 3科A*報下睇睇？"},{"pid":"4a749af6c273657c77fe6a4036acca3f0573ce76","tid":2215282,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4686c7608eb528066590a4742c77b8bc6f3467","tid":2215282,"uid":368082,"like":0,"disli